                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The skeletal Hellknight bonesinger strikes its rib cage three times, creating a loud, ominous clatter. All mindless skeletons in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:30] must use their reaction to Stride closer to the bonesinger.</p>"
